title: Newblue Video Essentials VI for Vegas Pro 13-XFORCE
description:
================
[INFO:]

Newblue Video Essentials VI for Vegas Pro 13-XFORCE | 5.31 MB

The best-selling Video Essentials, offers 100 presets in 10 incredibly sophisticated plugins. Using Video Essentials VI, you can effortlessly call attention to a particular section of your footage, remove subtle imperfections while retaining strong detail, align multi-track picture-in-pictures, replicate your footage into a video wall, or instantly replace one color for another. Achieve these professional effects and more with ease using Video Essentials VI.

Platform : Windows XP/Vista/Windows 7/Windows 8/Windows 8.1
Language : English


================
[INSTALL NOTES:]
================

0.Install Vegas Pro
1.Install NewBlueFX Addon for Vegas Pro
2.Disable net Connection
3.Import reg file with admin rights
4.Start Vegas Pro, first time you select a newblue fx
 a serial prompt will pop up, use the keygen to finish
 the offline registration
 
5.That's it, Enjoy it

NOTE: Keygens, patches, Activators, Cracks, Loaders etc. are always scanned with
     Kaspersky Internet Security 2014 Latest Version to Avoid Virus
     issues.
